query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `projects` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `organizationId` int NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `type` enum('assessment', 'implementation', 'audit', 'consulting', 'training') NOT NULL,
  `status` enum('lead', 'proposal', 'contracted', 'kickoff', 'in_progress', 'review', 'completed', 'cancelled') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'lead',
  `priority` enum('low', 'medium', 'high', 'urgent') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'medium',
  `packageId` int,
  `subscriptionId` int,
  `projectManagerId` int,
  `leadLawyerId` int,
  `leadConsultantId` int,
  `startDate` timestamp,
  `dueDate` timestamp,
  `completedDate` timestamp,
  `estimatedHours` int,
  `actualHours` int,
  `budget` decimal(10, 2),
  `actualCost` decimal(10, 2),
  `progress` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `scope` text,
  `deliverables` text,
  `notes` text,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  INDEX `organization_idx` (`organizationId`),
  INDEX `status_idx` (`status`),
  INDEX `project_manager_idx` (`projectManagerId`)
)
